MECHANIC'S LIEN
STATE OF NEVADA
COUNTY OF NYE
1.
Gene M Parker (the "Claimant"), located at 1220 Dysart Dr, Banning, California 92220,
claims a mechanics lien for the labor or services or equipment or materials described herein,
furnished for a work of improvement on that certain real property located in the County of Nye, in
the State of Nevada. The complete address of the real property on which this mechanics lien is
claimed is: 231 Charleston View Ave, Pahrump, Nevada 89060 (the "Property"). The permanent
index identification number of the Property is: 029-231-12. The legal description of the Property
is:
SW1/4 NW1/4 19S 53E 15
1.2 acre
2.
The labor or services or equipment or materials were furnished by Claimant at the request
of: Pahrump Container Project LLC, located at 550 Front St Unit 2304, San Diego, California
92101.
3.
The owner of the Property is: Pahrump Container Project LLC, located at 550 Front St
Unit 2304, San Diego, California 92101.
4.
On 07/01/2020, the Claimant entered into an oral contract to provide material, labor and
equipment for home construction projects on said Property (the "Contract") for the original total
sum of $90,000.00, which became due and payable on 3-23-21, the date of completion of the
build and/or project services.
